Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.objects.road

Class SimpleRoadPosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.objects.road.SimpleRoadPosition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IRoadPosition
    public class SimpleRoadPosition
extends Object
implements IRoadPosition
    Default implementation io IRoadPosition which holds the raw data from the traffic simulation. Some of the getters return null values, as the information is missing at this state. The application simulator, which knows much more about the road topology, uses this incomplete data to identify the road items and can provide more data to the applications.
